asset.author: TeslaMotors
asset.hookText:
Experience the test drive day of the model S. We take you not only trough the test drive but have a chance to ask these guys some questions. So wether your considering buying either the stock or the car this is a must see. I truly came back believing that this car performed better than any other gas powered car in its class. I think the key to this unique drive is the low center of gravity that gives a grip that no combustion engine car can physically achieve.


When I bought AAPL apple the day Steve Jobs got rehired in 1997 at 4 buck equivalent and accumulated, back then everyone and there mom bashed the company, look at it now. Im a full time stock and options trader, yet all my trading trough the years has﻿ not made me as much money as holding on to AAPL stock from 4 buck equivalent after stock splits. I feel about TSLA today as I felt about AAPL back then. Time will tell if I'm right
